      "role": "user",
      "content": "friend or family? they don't get it. they just tell me \"time heals everything\" or \"you'll move on.\" it's so patronizing. they aren't the ones living in this silence. it feels like i'm just waiting for something that's never coming back, and the waiting is the worst part. it's exhausting to even exist right now.",
